videos.description: Elijah Long breaks down the defense then gives the no look dime to Chris Wray who finishes with the layup for Mt St. Mary's.
videos.headline: Mt St. Mary's Long with the no-look assist leading to a layup

videos.description: 5'5 Junior Robinson attacks the basket and makes the smooth layup for Mt St. Mary's.
videos.headline: Mt St. Mary's  Robinson attacks the rim for the layup

videos.description: Junior Robinson goes in for the layup but Josh Nebo denies him for St Francis PA.
videos.headline: St Francis (PA) Nebo gets up high for the block

videos.description: Mt St. Mary's beats St. Francis PA to earn a trip to the NCAA tournament.
videos.headline: Mt St. Mary's punches its ticket to the NCAA Tournament

videos.description: Elijah Long talks about what his team did right to punch a ticket to the NCAA Tournament.
videos.headline: Elijah Long talks about his teams comeback victory
